WEBVTT

00:00:29.579 --> 00:00:29.800
Well,

00:00:29.820 --> 00:00:32.162
welcome to our library studio and our

00:00:32.203 --> 00:00:34.987
continuing presentation of The Last Word

00:00:35.027 --> 00:00:35.448
Picture.

00:00:36.408 --> 00:00:37.250
And in so doing,

00:00:37.289 --> 00:00:39.311
we are going to now begin our review,

00:00:40.173 --> 00:00:41.435
hopefully for the last time,

00:00:42.676 --> 00:00:43.537
although who knows,

00:00:43.978 --> 00:00:45.299
as much as we're learning from it,

00:00:46.021 --> 00:00:48.183
of the Eighty-Ninth Mizmowr Series.

00:00:50.997 --> 00:00:54.098
I used to say that exuberantly until I

00:00:54.139 --> 00:00:56.959
realized the role that I've had in

00:00:57.439 --> 00:00:58.820
composing it with Yahowah.

00:00:59.359 --> 00:01:02.060
And so I'm a little more cautious in

00:01:02.119 --> 00:01:02.679
saying that,

00:01:02.799 --> 00:01:04.721
although that is still my conclusion,

00:01:04.760 --> 00:01:07.081
that it is the most important piece of

00:01:07.141 --> 00:01:09.861
literature that we will find among the

00:01:09.881 --> 00:01:11.701
Towrah prophets and Psalms.

00:01:12.802 --> 00:01:14.561
It was comprised, as we know,

00:01:14.602 --> 00:01:16.543
in a collaboration between Yahowah and a

00:01:16.582 --> 00:01:18.882
man named Ethan ha 'Ezrachy.

00:01:20.534 --> 00:01:24.516
Ethan ha 'Ezrachy defines a character that has

00:01:25.117 --> 00:01:27.298
been part of God's story for a very

00:01:27.378 --> 00:01:28.259
long time.

00:01:28.819 --> 00:01:30.060
As of this moment,

00:01:30.120 --> 00:01:33.760
he is fifty-four hundred years old in

00:01:33.820 --> 00:01:36.862
terms of the initiation of his soul.

00:01:36.923 --> 00:01:40.405
He was originally Chanowk, Enoch,

00:01:41.105 --> 00:01:44.626
and he has made many visits here over

00:01:44.686 --> 00:01:45.046
time.

00:01:48.012 --> 00:01:49.352
Well, one of his most important,

00:01:49.373 --> 00:01:51.954
and maybe it is his most important,

00:01:51.995 --> 00:01:55.899
was here in collaboration with the Yahowah to

00:01:56.179 --> 00:02:01.804
resolve the really identity crisis that

00:02:02.323 --> 00:02:03.385
was plaguing Dowd.

00:02:04.006 --> 00:02:09.450
Dowd became far too interested in the

00:02:11.359 --> 00:02:15.960
lust of life as opposed to the love

00:02:16.120 --> 00:02:18.100
of his life, who was Yahowah.

00:02:19.100 --> 00:02:23.581
He became belligerent against God.

00:02:23.602 --> 00:02:24.582
In fact,

00:02:24.842 --> 00:02:26.242
I'm going to share something with you in

00:02:26.263 --> 00:02:27.824
this psalm that I never thought I would

00:02:27.843 --> 00:02:30.243
ever come to this position because I have

00:02:30.283 --> 00:02:32.944
such a low regard for Adam and such

00:02:32.985 --> 00:02:34.284
a high regard for Dowd.

00:02:34.824 --> 00:02:36.385
But as we consider how

00:02:38.350 --> 00:02:41.292
lethargic Dowd became when he was lounging

00:02:41.312 --> 00:02:45.612
around all day while his subjects were off

00:02:45.832 --> 00:02:49.813
fighting a war and how he became a

00:02:49.854 --> 00:02:51.993
voyeur and an alcoholic.

00:02:52.174 --> 00:02:55.955
And then when given the chance to come

00:02:55.995 --> 00:02:58.155
clean and resolve these problems,

00:02:58.675 --> 00:03:01.316
doubled down and passed blame to God,

00:03:01.675 --> 00:03:03.377
took no responsibility for it.

00:03:04.016 --> 00:03:04.717
He reminds me

00:03:05.953 --> 00:03:10.235
a lot in this particular mode of Adam

00:03:10.414 --> 00:03:10.955
long ago.

00:03:12.036 --> 00:03:15.358
And so this was a real crisis of

00:03:15.437 --> 00:03:15.937
identity.

00:03:16.959 --> 00:03:17.938
It had to be resolved.

00:03:19.060 --> 00:03:20.881
Had it not been resolved,

00:03:22.361 --> 00:03:24.002
essentially the human experiment would

00:03:24.022 --> 00:03:25.302
have come to a crashing halt.

00:03:25.342 --> 00:03:28.745
There'd have been no opportunity for the

00:03:28.764 --> 00:03:31.667
fulfillment of Pesach, Matsah and Bikuwrym.

00:03:33.007 --> 00:03:33.587
And with the

00:03:34.727 --> 00:03:36.067
Mowedym, unfulfilled,

00:03:36.888 --> 00:03:40.568
there'd be no chance of establishing the

00:03:40.609 --> 00:03:45.490
covenant or of anyone living past this

00:03:45.849 --> 00:03:47.390
life, including Dowd.

00:03:48.431 --> 00:03:50.391
And so it becomes...

00:03:52.018 --> 00:03:54.621
One of the most essential interventions of

00:03:54.681 --> 00:03:55.281
all time.

00:03:55.661 --> 00:03:57.703
This is particularly true because Dowd and

00:03:57.742 --> 00:04:01.306
Yahowah were no longer on a talkative basis.

00:04:01.387 --> 00:04:04.149
They had stepped apart from one another.

00:04:04.830 --> 00:04:07.551
Yahowah only communicated to Dowd through an

00:04:07.592 --> 00:04:09.354
intermediary, that being Nathan.

00:04:09.873 --> 00:04:10.634
And even here,

00:04:10.715 --> 00:04:12.635
the Eighty-Ninth Mizmowr is being

00:04:12.675 --> 00:04:16.019
delivered by Ethan  ha 'Ezrachy,

00:04:16.220 --> 00:04:18.762
not spoken directly to Dowd.

00:04:20.788 --> 00:04:22.408
And so to resolve that problem,

00:04:22.507 --> 00:04:24.028
God had an ingenious plan.

00:04:24.149 --> 00:04:28.048
That plan involved him inserting a man and

00:04:28.069 --> 00:04:29.410
woman, a husband and wife,

00:04:29.509 --> 00:04:31.490
who would serve as surrogate parents,

00:04:31.670 --> 00:04:32.709
father and mother,

00:04:34.069 --> 00:04:35.350
for the very son of God,

00:04:35.651 --> 00:04:37.591
for the most important man who ever lived,

00:04:37.651 --> 00:04:39.271
the king of Israel,

00:04:39.870 --> 00:04:44.992
to restore his relationship with Yahowah so

00:04:45.012 --> 00:04:48.333
that he could recover from his tragic

00:04:48.353 --> 00:04:48.452
death.

00:04:49.403 --> 00:04:50.483
Mistake in judgment,

00:04:51.646 --> 00:04:56.791
come to embrace his destiny and fulfill in

00:04:56.851 --> 00:04:58.994
a second of three lives, Pesach, Matsah,

00:04:59.014 --> 00:04:59.514
and Bikuwrym.

00:05:00.014 --> 00:05:01.156
So this was the challenge.

00:05:01.776 --> 00:05:04.160
And the document that caused it to happen

00:05:04.420 --> 00:05:06.201
was the Eighty-Ninth Mizmowr.

00:05:06.423 --> 00:05:08.185
It is being delivered to Dowd.

00:05:10.103 --> 00:05:12.423
sometime after his, uh,

00:05:12.463 --> 00:05:14.646
fifty-sixth birthday,

00:05:14.906 --> 00:05:17.206
and I would say probably, um,

00:05:18.288 --> 00:05:20.870
right around his sixtieth year.

00:05:22.983 --> 00:05:23.204
You know,

00:05:23.223 --> 00:05:25.785
things went south for Dowd even after this

00:05:25.884 --> 00:05:27.305
Bathsheba incident.

00:05:27.346 --> 00:05:31.668
He suffered all manner of calamities,

00:05:32.168 --> 00:05:34.170
and I don't think they were resolved

00:05:34.230 --> 00:05:34.670
quickly.

00:05:34.750 --> 00:05:38.391
So I would suspect that Dowd was over

00:05:38.451 --> 00:05:41.752
sixty by the time that he was visited

00:05:41.812 --> 00:05:45.894
by his surrogate parents and this manner

00:05:46.074 --> 00:05:50.757
of rebellion against his father, Yahowah.

00:05:51.774 --> 00:05:53.055
was resolved.

00:05:54.137 --> 00:05:56.017
What we're going to hear in this Mizmowr

00:05:57.298 --> 00:06:00.422
is, initially, Ethan ha 'Ezrachy ,

00:06:01.442 --> 00:06:04.685
speaking about God's character,

00:06:05.505 --> 00:06:06.105
his nature.

00:06:06.786 --> 00:06:11.250
He's going to introduce what he deems to

00:06:11.290 --> 00:06:13.132
be Yahowah's most important

00:06:13.172 --> 00:06:16.795
characteristics, loyalty, devotion,

00:06:17.634 --> 00:06:18.055
and love.

00:06:18.978 --> 00:06:22.761
along with trustworthiness, integrity,

00:06:23.701 --> 00:06:24.802
and reliability.

00:06:28.264 --> 00:06:31.745
Probably four times over in his

00:06:31.805 --> 00:06:32.846
presentation of Yahowah,

00:06:32.867 --> 00:06:35.548
and he's doing so because his message to

00:06:35.608 --> 00:06:40.670
Dowd has no merit apart from Yahowah's

00:06:40.810 --> 00:06:41.870
inspiration of it.

00:06:42.612 --> 00:06:45.372
It all hinges on who Yahowah is.

00:06:46.653 --> 00:06:48.194
Ethan is the delivery boy.

00:06:49.127 --> 00:06:50.507
He is, well, the delivery man.

00:06:50.567 --> 00:06:52.408
He's serving his father at this point.

00:06:53.249 --> 00:06:58.389
But he is conveying this message from

00:07:01.170 --> 00:07:03.052
Yahowah to his son.

00:07:03.091 --> 00:07:04.872
And the only way that it has credibility

00:07:04.932 --> 00:07:08.413
is to acknowledge Yahowah's credibility and

00:07:08.454 --> 00:07:09.353
devotion to his son,

00:07:09.555 --> 00:07:11.194
his steadfastness in this regard.

00:07:12.336 --> 00:07:13.375
In the early statements,

00:07:13.396 --> 00:07:15.437
we're going to find Ethan talk about

00:07:15.476 --> 00:07:15.857
himself.

00:07:17.057 --> 00:07:19.819
and who he represents so that Dowd

00:07:19.858 --> 00:07:22.500
understands that the man speaking to him

00:07:23.781 --> 00:07:27.663
isn't one of his subjects.

00:07:27.684 --> 00:07:31.427
He is very close to Dowd's equal.

00:07:33.247 --> 00:07:34.649
He has skin in the game.

00:07:36.410 --> 00:07:38.591
He is one who will suffer as Dowd

00:07:38.632 --> 00:07:39.172
has suffered.

00:07:39.451 --> 00:07:41.353
He will fulfill the Mow'ed Miqra'ey.

00:07:41.733 --> 00:07:43.814
He will write as Dowd has written.

00:07:44.014 --> 00:07:46.117
He will lead as Dowd has led.

00:07:47.523 --> 00:07:50.185
He will be inspired as Dowd was inspired.

00:07:51.846 --> 00:07:54.427
He is as close to Dowd as anyone

00:07:56.048 --> 00:08:00.271
will or has ever been.

00:08:00.350 --> 00:08:04.274
And so he talks about himself and he

00:08:04.314 --> 00:08:07.175
does so to garner Dowd's attention and

00:08:07.196 --> 00:08:07.596
trust.

00:08:08.916 --> 00:08:10.398
For Dowd to know he is not in

00:08:10.497 --> 00:08:10.778
this

00:08:13.451 --> 00:08:15.012
And the earlier program in the Ocean

00:08:15.033 --> 00:08:15.853
Studio today,

00:08:16.033 --> 00:08:18.132
I hinted at something that even my wife

00:08:18.173 --> 00:08:19.733
came in just a few minutes ago and

00:08:19.774 --> 00:08:19.973
said,

00:08:20.194 --> 00:08:22.413
what in the world were you talking about

00:08:22.494 --> 00:08:23.915
at the end of that show?

00:08:25.675 --> 00:08:32.775
Where I said that it's my conclusion based

00:08:32.816 --> 00:08:35.037
upon what I'm hearing in the Twelfth

00:08:35.096 --> 00:08:36.476
Mizmowr,

00:08:37.356 --> 00:08:39.618
that it is highly likely

00:08:41.613 --> 00:08:45.635
that when Yahowah allowed Dowd to fulfill

00:08:45.696 --> 00:08:48.477
his destiny and to serve as the Pesach

00:08:48.618 --> 00:08:51.879
Ayil and then take our guilt into Sheowl

00:08:52.961 --> 00:08:57.203
on Matsah, that he did not go alone.

00:09:00.626 --> 00:09:06.510
Once Yahowah brought Leah and I in,

00:09:07.072 --> 00:09:08.873
and this is Leah and I,

00:09:11.158 --> 00:09:15.022
to support Dowd at this time in this

00:09:15.101 --> 00:09:15.461
way.

00:09:17.323 --> 00:09:19.725
We bonded with him as no one else

00:09:19.764 --> 00:09:20.385
in his life.

00:09:21.066 --> 00:09:23.668
We essentially became his mother and

00:09:23.688 --> 00:09:24.009
father.

00:09:25.490 --> 00:09:27.692
And there is no way in the world

00:09:28.251 --> 00:09:32.456
that we would have allowed him to go

00:09:32.535 --> 00:09:33.616
fulfill Pesach,

00:09:34.636 --> 00:09:36.798
Matsah and Bikuwrym in his second of three

00:09:36.839 --> 00:09:39.201
lives alone.

00:09:41.919 --> 00:09:46.481
And so there is the high likelihood that

00:09:46.522 --> 00:09:46.981
we were there.

00:09:47.861 --> 00:09:49.263
And I did, in the break,

00:09:50.062 --> 00:09:53.203
in addition to continuing to translate and

00:09:53.244 --> 00:09:55.325
work upon the Eighty-Ninth Mizmowr,

00:09:55.345 --> 00:09:59.025
I'm a little over just quite,

00:09:59.086 --> 00:10:01.147
not quite two-thirds finished with it.

00:10:01.187 --> 00:10:02.167
We're going to start here with the

00:10:02.187 --> 00:10:03.527
dedication in this program.

00:10:03.586 --> 00:10:04.788
So at least I'm ahead of where we

00:10:04.807 --> 00:10:05.587
are on this program.

00:10:06.969 --> 00:10:10.789
I did turn to the Twenty-Second Mizmowr.

00:10:12.371 --> 00:10:12.912
And I was right.

00:10:16.414 --> 00:10:17.615
I think we were there,

00:10:18.475 --> 00:10:21.357
but most certainly I was there to support

00:10:21.778 --> 00:10:23.558
Dowd.

00:10:23.639 --> 00:10:25.179
And so with that in mind,

00:10:25.240 --> 00:10:29.162
I'd like to introduce this marvelous song

00:10:29.201 --> 00:10:29.503
again.

00:10:29.743 --> 00:10:31.423
I've always considered it to be Dowd's

00:10:31.443 --> 00:10:31.703
song.

00:10:32.303 --> 00:10:34.846
It was composed for him,

00:10:35.446 --> 00:10:37.067
but it's also composed for us.

00:10:37.187 --> 00:10:40.870
It is a song that completely destroys

00:10:41.988 --> 00:10:44.070
Christianity, Judaism, and Islam.

00:10:45.169 --> 00:10:47.692
And only someone who has spent the time

00:10:47.711 --> 00:10:50.313
that I have repudiating those religions,

00:10:50.595 --> 00:10:52.196
having written thirteen books,

00:10:52.716 --> 00:10:54.456
each averaging about seven hundred and

00:10:54.477 --> 00:10:55.357
fifty pages,

00:10:57.078 --> 00:10:59.541
citing a comparison between God's

00:10:59.581 --> 00:11:03.825
testimony and the false prophecy of

00:11:04.764 --> 00:11:07.847
Judaism, Islam, and Christianity.

00:11:08.631 --> 00:11:11.173
would be able to fully appreciate just how

00:11:11.373 --> 00:11:14.794
devastating this Eighty-Ninth Mizmowr is

00:11:15.154 --> 00:11:16.015
to those religions.

00:11:16.076 --> 00:11:17.416
They don't survive it.

00:11:17.996 --> 00:11:21.057
This eviscerates them.

00:11:21.217 --> 00:11:23.678
And it's why I quoted it in all

00:11:23.720 --> 00:11:24.000
of them,

00:11:24.419 --> 00:11:27.240
because it is essential to negating them.

00:11:29.302 --> 00:11:31.383
But it also establishes exactly who Dowd

00:11:31.423 --> 00:11:31.562
is.

00:11:33.484 --> 00:11:34.485
He is the Son of God.

00:11:35.325 --> 00:11:36.605
He is the anointed Messiah.

00:11:37.573 --> 00:11:39.375
He is the Passover lamb and therefore our

00:11:39.414 --> 00:11:39.816
savior.

00:11:40.395 --> 00:11:41.356
He is the chosen one.

00:11:42.037 --> 00:11:45.000
He is the one through whom the covenant

00:11:45.080 --> 00:11:51.644
was literally established.

00:11:51.684 --> 00:11:54.346
It's extraordinary what it says of him.

00:11:54.407 --> 00:11:56.347
He was the one through whom God chose

00:11:56.388 --> 00:11:57.509
to work, his coworker.

00:11:58.789 --> 00:12:01.851
It leaves no room for anyone else in

00:12:01.892 --> 00:12:02.493
that regard.

00:12:05.134 --> 00:12:06.434
So now that we know the identity of

00:12:06.455 --> 00:12:08.517
the man conveying Dowd's song and

00:12:08.876 --> 00:12:10.638
collaborating in the writing of it on

00:12:10.697 --> 00:12:11.818
behalf of his father,

00:12:12.700 --> 00:12:14.701
and his collaboration, by the way,

00:12:15.121 --> 00:12:20.044
takes us through about the first fifteen

00:12:20.144 --> 00:12:21.667
or so statements,

00:12:21.746 --> 00:12:24.288
maybe closer to twenty statements.

00:12:25.071 --> 00:12:28.032
When there is one and the first twenty,

00:12:28.072 --> 00:12:31.852
there is one statement that's directly

00:12:31.913 --> 00:12:32.513
from Yahowah.

00:12:32.753 --> 00:12:34.773
It just come out with a kaboom.

00:12:34.812 --> 00:12:35.894
This is who Dowd is.

00:12:36.774 --> 00:12:41.995
And then it says some remarkable things

00:12:42.034 --> 00:12:45.515
that I had no knowledge of prior.

00:12:46.336 --> 00:12:49.336
That brings us to today about the things

00:12:49.376 --> 00:12:51.977
that Yahowah will do through Ethan

00:12:52.018 --> 00:12:52.638
ha 'Ezrachy.

00:12:54.013 --> 00:12:55.634
And then after he explains that,

00:12:58.355 --> 00:12:59.754
God picks up the narrative.

00:13:00.775 --> 00:13:03.476
And for in the range of twenty statements

00:13:03.517 --> 00:13:06.477
in a row, everyone is in Yahowah's voice.

00:13:07.498 --> 00:13:09.399
And so that is the pace of this.

00:13:12.279 --> 00:13:14.400
Ethan ha 'Ezrachy does the introduction.

00:13:14.880 --> 00:13:15.961
He tells us about Yahowah.

00:13:16.381 --> 00:13:17.461
He tells us about himself.

00:13:18.822 --> 00:13:21.884
Yahowah makes a profoundly important

00:13:21.923 --> 00:13:23.825
declaration about Dowd.

00:13:24.571 --> 00:13:29.773
And then we return to Ethan describing

00:13:30.072 --> 00:13:34.114
what he knows of Yahowah and what he

00:13:34.195 --> 00:13:37.796
perceives of Dowd and what he will do

00:13:37.916 --> 00:13:39.876
in his life in support of him.

00:13:41.537 --> 00:13:46.678
And then we turn to full blast Yahowah.

00:13:47.479 --> 00:13:48.659
It becomes...

00:13:49.780 --> 00:13:52.442
amazingly brilliant i thought that the

00:13:52.462 --> 00:13:54.825
parts that i had written were reasonably

00:13:54.865 --> 00:13:58.187
astute but god is infinitely more

00:13:58.547 --> 00:14:01.149
articulate he is just let me tell you

00:14:01.168 --> 00:14:04.892
the way it is so it's time now

00:14:04.912 --> 00:14:06.952
that we venture back into the ultimate

00:14:06.993 --> 00:14:09.715
Mizmowr the greatest song ever sung i see

00:14:09.735 --> 00:14:11.535
it not only as the cornerstone of the

00:14:11.576 --> 00:14:14.778
covenant and it indeed is and of Yahowah's

00:14:14.818 --> 00:14:17.900
home on earth but it's also the keystone

00:14:18.761 --> 00:14:18.902
of

00:14:19.726 --> 00:14:21.927
God's message and my mission.

00:14:22.807 --> 00:14:24.847
I think it was inspired and written

00:14:27.548 --> 00:14:30.730
sometime at least eight years before the

00:14:30.809 --> 00:14:34.311
sixtieth Yowbel year in three thousand

00:14:34.331 --> 00:14:34.650
years,

00:14:35.510 --> 00:14:36.910
but it could have been written as early

00:14:36.951 --> 00:14:38.511
as fourteen years.

00:14:39.465 --> 00:14:40.405
prior to that time,

00:14:40.966 --> 00:14:44.629
and therefore on or around the sixtieth

00:14:44.828 --> 00:14:48.172
birthday of Dowd when he was sixty years

00:14:48.251 --> 00:14:48.412
old.

00:14:48.951 --> 00:14:53.375
He would end his first of three lives

00:14:53.875 --> 00:14:54.635
at seventy.

00:14:55.157 --> 00:14:56.638
So at sixty,

00:14:56.758 --> 00:14:58.860
